 <div class="review-div" id="rev4">
    <h2>"Pride and Prejudice" (2005)</h2>
   <p><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0414387/">Pride & Prejudice</a>, directed by Joe Wright, is a sweeping yet intimate adaptation of Pride and Prejudice by Jane Austen. With its windswept landscapes, candlelit interiors, and emotionally charged performances, the film reimagines Austen’s classic romance for a modern audience while preserving its wit and social insight.</p>
